<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạ̉kẖṭạ̉t lyk gẖfrt ly - qsyt ʿlyk ḥnyt ʿly bʿdt ʿnk jdẖbtny - frbt mnk ạsrtny ạlqrạr - ạnạ dạyb blmstk mdywn wtạyb brḥmtk msẖtạq lẓlk wʿsẖrtk ygẖslny qrbk wrḍạk 2- jryt ʿlyk wḥạly ḥạl - sjdt lyk wdmʿy sạl bdạ̉t ạḥky wḥkạy ṭạl - smʿt ṣwtk mạ tkẖạf tʿạl 3- bạḥb tsẖkyl ạnạỷy byk - ạ̉ṣlh lqrby wqdạsty fyk wqthạ ḥḍnk dạymạ ykwn - mljạ̉ ly tẖạbt wsṭ ạlạ̉twn 4- yạ qlby gẖny bạlly fdạk - wḥdh bḥbh ạsr hwạk gẖslny dmh fk ạlqywd - dʿạny ạbnh bdwn ḥdwd</lyrics>
